cs.PL, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.SE 

The paper discusses applications of logic programming, which is a subfield of programming languages (cs.PL). The three key abstractions discussed in the paper (join, recursion, and constraint) are commonly used in database queries (cs.DB), inductive analysis (cs.AI), and combinatorial search (cs.LO). The paper also briefly touches on programming paradigms and systems, which are relevant to software engineering (cs.SE).
